* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.fit binary
*.zip binary
*.parquet binary

# The adopted Platform Standard uses Markdown two-space hard breaks. Preserve
# those files byte-for-byte while keeping normal whitespace checks elsewhere.
PLATFORM_EVOLUTION.md whitespace=-blank-at-eol
QUICK_START.md whitespace=-blank-at-eol
docs/project_os/** whitespace=-blank-at-eol
docs/proofs/** whitespace=-blank-at-eol
runtime/work/** whitespace=-blank-at-eol
docs/README.md whitespace=-blank-at-eof
